reviewText: Outstanding, like Vander Laan's other series.  Meaningful, eye-opening, an excellent way to refresh your faith.
Love the Ray Vander Laan Teaching.
So many deep Bible lessons. Vander Laan presents the Bible in historical context so you understand it all with new insights.

Our SS class is studying it right now and we plan to study another.
The video really gives a lot of in site about the life in the days of Christ.

Ray Vander Laan is a teacher I would like to have had my children and grandchildren have in school.  What insights!  Oh how I wish I could go on a tour with him leading.  Absolutely having the entire 12 dvd's is a must for my library.
Were good about keeping me updated on the progress of shipment. Item arrived early. Item was exactly as advertised. Would use them again.
